We'll need our other return value test trick here, as you need to check the extracted values are valid before you use them:

```
if ((rc = pldm_msgbuf_extract(dst, entity_type)) ||
    (rc = pldm_msgbuf_extract(dst, entity_instance_num) ||
    (rc = pldm_msgbuf_extract(dts, entity_container_id)) {
    return rc;
}
```
